actions.message: To easily understand what armor any bullet can penetrate you divide the bullets pen value by 10 and the result is what armor class the bullet will penetrate. Example: 7N39 Igolnik has 62 in pen value and divide that by 10 and you get 6.2 so that means that the bullet is powerful enough to go through any armor in the game at the moment because the highest class for armors is 6.
